JO  - Cyber Security (CyberSecurity), 2012 International Conference on
TI  - I Have the Proof: Providing Proofs of Past Data Possession in Cloud Forensics
T2  - Cyber Security (CyberSecurity), 2012 International Conference on
IS  - 
