TY  - CONF
JO  - Services Computing (SCC), 2010 IEEE International Conference on
TI  - Accountability as a Service for the Cloud
T2  - Services Computing (SCC), 2010 IEEE International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 81
EP  - 88
AU  - Jinhui Yao
