JO  - Information Assurance and Security (IAS), 2010 Sixth International Conference on
TI  - Reconciling IHE-ATNA profile with a posteriori contextual access and usage control policy in healthcare environment
T2  - Information Assurance and Security (IAS), 2010 Sixth International Conference on
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 197
EP  - 203
AU  - Azkia, H.
