TI  - Trees Cannot Lie: Using Data Structures for Forensics Purposes
T2  - Intelligence and Security Informatics Conference (EISIC), 2011 European
IS  - 
SN  - 
VO  - 
SP  - 282
EP  - 285
AU  - Kieseberg, P.
